    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>我描绘出，难以忘记的，回忆的片段。</p></blockquote><span id="more"></span>        <h1 id="衔接班生活">          <a href="#衔接班生活" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#衔接班生活"></a> 衔接班生活</h1>      <p><em>谨以此文，记录我在衔接班的生活趣事。</em></p><p><em>为尊重个人隐私，文中姓名均以首字母缩写或网名代替，请勿打扰任何出现在文中的朋友。</em></p>        <h2 id="暑假">          <a href="#暑假" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#暑假"></a> 暑假</h2>              <h3 id="分班考试">          <a href="#分班考试" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#分班考试"></a> 分班考试</h3>      <p>作为一个初来乍到的衔接班学生，自然是要参加分班考试的。当然如果你是去参见 NOI 的 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>longer_name</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{longer\_name}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">longer_name</span></span></span></span></span> 的话，你就可以以时间冲突为由直接咕掉。</p><p>考试顺序我已经完全忘记，当我想起这段往事时，只是在脑海中浮现出了一些若隐若现的细节。</p><p>语文是 zyq 监考的，考试时间是 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>1.5h</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{1.5h}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">1.5h</span></span></span></span></span> 。我觉得不算很难，倒是忘记了“衣冠简朴古风存”的上句。英语倒是非常难，还有 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>15</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">15</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord">5</span></span></span></span> 分的用英语描述一下学习情况，但是因为我<strong>英语太差了</strong>没读懂题面，所以肯定白给了。估计到时候文科会成为我衔接班生活的一大困难。</p><p>数学和物理我倒是认为很简单。数学剩了半小时睡觉，期间监考老师 zk 还来翻了一遍我的卷子。有趣的是， zk 在看完我的答案以后去他自己的卷子上做了个标记，我也不知道什么意思。物理直接轻松拿下，然后生物博物选择直接摆烂，然后考试就结束了。</p><p>成绩发布，<strong>除了英语</strong>都在平均分上，物理更是远超平均分 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>30</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">30</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span> 分。我直呼轻松拿下，认为衔接班考试也是小菜一碟，轻轻松松。但这时，我还没意识到衔接班考试的可怖之处。</p>        <h3 id="正睿集训">          <a href="#正睿集训" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#正睿集训"></a> 正睿集训</h3>      <p>本来说的是下午直接飞 ZJ 去上 ZR 的课，结果 BJ 突然疫情然后直接把行程 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>ban</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{ban}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">ban</span></span></span></span></span> 了，希望没事。</p><p>题很难 <strong>qwq</strong> ，一般模拟赛就只会打暴力，但是暴力打满其实排名很高。有几天摆烂不想打就没开题，这样就可以保 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>rating</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{rating}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8623000000000001em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">rating</span></span></span></span></span> 。但是当 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Crabby</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Crabby}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Crabby</span></span></span></span></span> 有一天看题太难了没打，然后白白掉了 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>300</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">300</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">3</span><span class="mord">0</span><span class="mord">0</span></span></span></span> 分，失声痛哭说“这是我<strong>好几天</strong> <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>rk1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{rk1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">rk1</span></span></span></span></span> 上的分啊！”的时候，我都有点被感动了（大雾）。</p><p>接下来便是多位重量级登场了。</p>        <h3 id="暑假集训">          <a href="#暑假集训" class="heading-link"><i class="fas fa-link"></i></a><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#暑假集训"></a> 暑假集训</h3>      <p>为了在之后的 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>CSP-S</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext>,</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext>NOIP</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{CSP-S\,,\,NOIP}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">CSP-S</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">NOIP</span></span></span></span></span> 中取得好成绩，我校开始了<strong>高强度全真模拟赛</strong>。<strong>高强度</strong>主要体现在“杭二”联测中我校金牌选手只会做 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn>1</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">1</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.64444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span></span></span></span> 道题，<strong>全真</strong>则体现在“乐多”赛制欢乐扣分。总之，在高强度全真模拟赛的训练下，我校成员的水平均得到了很大的提升，具体提升了什么呢？我们来看下面几段实况。</p><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Dark_night</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Dark\_night}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Dark_night</span></span></span></span></span> ：我这加了快读快写怎么还会 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>TLE</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{TLE}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">TLE</span></span></span></span></span> 啊？<br>复盘：使用 <code>printf</code> 进行快速输出（</p><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Kardashev</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Kardashev}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Kardashev</span></span></span></span></span> ：我为什么 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>RE</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{RE}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">RE</span></span></span></span></span> 力！<br>复盘：数据范围 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>≤</mo><mn>2</mn><mo>×</mo><mn>1</mn><msup><mn>0</mn><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">n \le 2 \times 10^5</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.7719400000000001em;vertical-align:-0.13597em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span><span class="mrel">≤</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2777777777777778em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.72777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord">2</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span><span class="mbin">×</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.2222222222222222em;"></span></span><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord">1</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord">0</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.8141079999999999em;"><span style="top:-3.063em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mtight">5</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> ，<code>int a[114514];</code></p><p>wyy ：我粘个快读快写板子。<br>xr ： wyy 你给板子删了。<br>wyy ：好。<br>几秒钟后……<br>wyy ： <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Ctrl+Z</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Ctrl+Z}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.77777em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Ctrl+Z</span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><p><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Sol1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Sol1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Sol1</span></span></span></span></span> ：在赛时，你可以通过大声敲键盘的方式来干扰坐在你旁边的选手；也可以写四个 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>A+B</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{A+B}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.76666em;vertical-align:-0.08333em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">A+B</span></span></span></span></span> 的对拍影响他们心态；你还可以……<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Dark_night</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Dark\_night}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Dark_night</span></span></span></span></span> ：……<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>juicy_name</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{juicy\_name}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.97786em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">juicy_name</span></span></span></span></span> ：……<br>（打联测中……）<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Sol1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Sol1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Sol1</span></span></span></span></span> ： <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>nice</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext>,</mtext><mtext> </mtext><mtext>AK</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{nice\,,\,AK}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8777699999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">nice</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">,</span><span class="mspace" style="margin-right:0.1667em;"></span><span class="mord">AK</span></span></span></span></span> 了!<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Dark_night</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Dark\_night}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Dark_night</span></span></span></span></span> ：(流汗黄豆)<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>juicy_name</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{juicy\_name}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.97786em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">juicy_name</span></span></span></span></span> ：***<br>赛后……<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Sol1</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Sol1}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.69444em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Sol1</span></span></span></span></span> 在博客中写道：小技巧非常好用，我左边的同学（ <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Dark_night</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Dark\_night}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Dark_night</span></span></span></span></span> ）不会做 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>T3</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{T3}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">T3</span></span></span></span></span> ，我右边的同学（ <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>juicy_name</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{juicy\_name}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.97786em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">juicy_name</span></span></span></span></span> ） <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>T4</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{T4}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.68333em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">T4</span></span></span></span></span> 没调完破防了……<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>Dark_night</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{Dark\_night}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1.00444em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">Dark_night</span></span></span></span></span> ：……<br><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mtext>juicy_name</mtext></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\text{juicy\_name}</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.97786em;vertical-align:-0.31em;"></span><span class="mord text"><span class="mord">juicy_name</span></span></span></span></span> ：……</p><p>（发现回忆录好长啊，明天接着写。）</p>]]></content>
    
    
